}

### Test 5: Bad request — missing nDirections
POST {{baseUrl}}/getFix
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "directionErrorModel": 0,
  "locations": [2.35, 48.86, 13.41, 52.52],
  "directions": [90, 225, 2, 2]
}
